trans-unit.source: Represents a key identifier clause that identifies a <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken"></xref> or <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"></xref> security token.
trans-unit.target: 表示密钥标识符子句，它标识<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken"></xref>或<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"></xref>安全令牌。

trans-unit.source: Use the KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause class to reference a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken> or <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken> security token using a SHA-1 hash of the Kerberos ticket.
trans-unit.target: 使用 KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause 类来引用<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>或<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken>使用 Kerberos 票证的 sha-1 哈希的安全令牌。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: The SHA-1 hash of the Kerberos ticket can be obtained by calling the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause.GetKerberosTicketHash%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 可以通过调用获取 Kerberos 票证的 sha-1 哈希<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause.GetKerberosTicketHash%2A>方法。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause.GetKerberosTicketHash%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"></xref> class using the specified SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"></xref>类使用 Kerberos 服务票证的指定的 sha-1 哈希。

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: 数组<xref:System.Byte>包含 Kerberos 服务票证的 sha-1 哈希。</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"></xref> class using the specified Kerberos ticket, nonce, and key length.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"></xref>类使用指定的 Kerberos 票证、 nonce 和密钥长度。

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)] does not support the creation of implied derived key identifiers.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)]不支持创建隐含的派生密钥标识符。

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)] processes and consumes incoming SOAP messages that contain implied derived key identifiers.
trans-unit.target: 但是，[!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)]处理和使用包含隐含派生密钥标识符的传入 SOAP 消息。

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: 数组<xref:System.Byte>包含 Kerberos 服务票证的 sha-1 哈希。</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the nonce that was used to create a derived key.
trans-unit.target: 数组<xref:System.Byte>，包含用于创建派生的密钥的 nonce。</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: The size of the derived key.
Gets the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: 获取 sha-1 哈希的 Kerberos 服务票证。

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: 数组<xref:System.Byte>包含 Kerberos 服务票证的 sha-1 哈希。</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: The ToString method returns the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: ToString 方法返回 sha-1 哈希的 Kerberos 服务票证。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the current object.
